forces always being 0. As such we recommend to use a Mujoco-Py version < 2.0","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"when using the Ant environment if you would like to report results with contact forces (if"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"contact forces are not used in your experiments, you can use version > 2.0)."}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]]],"header":"row","type":"table"},{"text":"Rewards","anchor":"Rewards","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The reward consists of three parts:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"healthy_reward","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":": Every timestep that the ant is healthy (see definition in section “Episode Termination”), it gets a reward of fixed value ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"healthy_reward"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"forward_reward","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":": A reward of moving forward which is measured as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(x-coordinate before action - x-coordinate after action)\/dt"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":". ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"dt"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" is the time","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"between actions and is dependent on the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"frame_skip"},{"text":" parameter (default is 5),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"where the frametime is 0.01 - making the default ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"dt = 5 * 0.01 = 0.05","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This reward would be positive if the ant moves forward (in positive x direction).","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"ctrl_cost","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":": A negative reward for penalising the ant if it takes actions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that are too large. It is measured as "},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"ctrl_cost_weight","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" * sum(action"},{"type":"text","text":"2"},{"type":"text","text":")"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"where "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ctr_cost_weight"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" is a parameter set for the control and has a default value of 0.5."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"contact_cost"}]},{"text":": A negative reward for penalising the ant if the external contact","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"force is too large. It is calculated ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"code":"contact_cost_weight","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" * sum(clip(external contact","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"force to ","type":"text"},{"code":"contact_force_range","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text":"2","type":"text"},{"text":")","type":"text"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The total reward returned is ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"reward","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"="}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"healthy_reward + forward_reward - ctrl_cost - contact_cost"}]},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"info"},{"text":" will also contain the individual reward terms.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Starting State","anchor":"Starting-State","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All observations start in state","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(0.0, 0.0,  0.75, 1.0, 0.0  … 0.0) with a uniform noise in the range","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of [-","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reset_noise_scale"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reset_noise_scale"},{"text":"] added to the positional values and standard normal noise","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with mean 0 and standard deviation ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reset_noise_scale"},{"text":" added to the velocity values for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"stochasticity. Note that the initial z coordinate is intentionally selected","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to be slightly high, thereby indicating a standing up ant. The initial orientation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is designed to make it face forward as well.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Episode End","anchor":"Episode-End","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The ant is said to be unhealthy if any of the following happens:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Any of the state space values is no longer finite","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The z-coordinate of the torso is ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"not"}]},{"text":" in the closed interval given by ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"healthy_z_range"},{"text":" (defaults to [0.2, 1.0])","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"terminate_when_unhealthy=True"},{"text":" is passed during construction (which is the default),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the episode ends when any of the following happens:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Truncation: The episode duration reaches a 1000 timesteps","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Termination: The ant is unhealthy"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"terminate_when_unhealthy=False"},{"type":"text","text":" is passed, the episode is ended only when 1000 timesteps are exceeded."}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"text":"Arguments","anchor":"Arguments","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"No additional arguments are currently supported in v2 and lower.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["env = gym.make('Ant-v2')"],"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"v3 and v4 take gym.make kwargs such as xml_file, ctrl_cost_weight, reset_noise_scale etc.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["env = gym.make('Ant-v4', ctrl_cost_weight=0.1, ...)"],"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing"},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Parameter","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Type"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Default","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"xml_file"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"str","type":"text"}]}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"ant.xml\""}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Path to a MuJoCo model"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ctrl_cost_weight"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"float"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0.5"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Weight for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"ctrl_cost","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" term (see section on reward)"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"contact_cost_weight","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"float","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"5e-4"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Weight for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"contact_cost","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" term (see section on reward)","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"healthy_reward"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"float"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"1","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Constant reward given if the ant is “healthy” after timestep","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"terminate_when_unhealthy","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"bool","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"True"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If true, issue a done signal if the z-coordinate of the torso is no longer in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"healthy_z_range"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"healthy_z_range","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"tuple","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"(0.2, 1)","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The ant is considered healthy if the z-coordinate of the torso is in this range"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"contact_force_range","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"tuple","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"(-1, 1)"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Contact forces are clipped to this range in the computation of ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"contact_cost","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reset_noise_scale"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"float"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0.1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Scale of random perturbations of initial position and velocity (see section on Starting State)"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"exclude_current_positions_from_observation"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"bool","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"True","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether or not to omit the x- and y-coordinates from observations. Excluding the position can serve as an inductive bias to induce position-agnostic behavior in policies"}]}]]],"header":"row","type":"table"},{"text":"Version History","anchor":"Version-History","type":"heading","level":3},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"v4: all mujoco environments now use the mujoco bindings in mujoco>=2.1.3","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"v3: support for gym.make kwargs such as xml_file, ctrl_cost_weight, reset_noise_scale etc. rgb rendering comes from tracking camera (so agent does not run away from screen)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"v2: All continuous control environments now use mujoco_py >= 1.50","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"v1: max_time_steps raised to 1000 for robot based tasks. Added reward_threshold to environments."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"v0: Initial versions release (1.0.0)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.liuliu.s4nnc\/documentation\/Gym\/Ant\/init(ctrlCostWeight:healthyReward:terminateWhenUnhealthy:healthyZRange:resetNoiseScale:)"]},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.liuliu.s4nnc\/documentation\/Gym\/Ant\/data","doc:\/\/org.liuliu.s4nnc\/documentation\/Gym\/Ant\/model"]},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.liuliu.s4nnc\/documentation\/Gym\/Ant\/Env-Implementations"],"generated":true}],"sections":[],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.liuliu.s4nnc\/documentation\/Gym\/Env","doc:\/\/org.liuliu.s4nnc\/documentation\/Gym\/MuJoCoEnv"],"kind":"relationships"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.liuliu.s4nnc\/documenta